This is `mbank-cli`, a command line interface to the on-line banking system of
mBank.

**Warning**: You use `mbank-cli` on your own risk!

**Warning**: `mbank-cli` is considered highly experimental. The interface is
likely to change in the near future.

**Warning**: `mbank-cli` uses the web interface at https://www.mbank.com.pl/
which is subject to change unexpectedly.


Requirements
------------

- Perl (≥ 5.10) with the following Perl modules:

  - Crypt::SSLeay

  - HTML::Form

  - HTML::Entities

  - HTTP::Cookies

  - LWP::UserAgent

- GNU Privacy Guard (optionally, to protect your password)

If you are using Debian, dependencies will be satisfied by the following packages:

- perl

- libcrypt-ssleay-perl

- libwww-perl

- gnupg


Usage
-----

For the complete syntax and usage examples, consult the manual page.


